{"tid":138097,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幼稚園老師：警察用暴力啱唔啱　梁美芬：係黑警","createTime":"2017-02-28T10:34:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T08:02:38.000Z","uid":47714,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"39942184b3f8f78626ff66311bdc9fa98b2e85cf","tid":138097,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:34:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/促立辱警罪-梁美芬重提佔領時有幼稚園老師教幼童-黑警-仇警/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%BF%83%E7%AB%8B%E8%BE%B1%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA-%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC%E9%87%8D%E6%8F%90%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E6%99%82%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E6%95%99%E5%B9%BC%E7%AB%A5-%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-%E4%BB%87%E8%AD%A6%2F&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67QKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=7a1ae50e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E4%BF%83%E7%AB%8B%E8%BE%B1%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%AA-%E6%A2%81%E7%BE%8E%E8%8A%AC%E9%87%8D%E6%8F%90%E4%BD%94%E9%A0%98%E6%99%82%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%BC%E7%A8%9A%E5%9C%92%E8%80%81%E5%B8%AB%E6%95%99%E5%B9%BC%E7%AB%A5-%E9%BB%91%E8%AD%A6-%E4%BB%87%E8%AD%A6%2F&h=31f1a184\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/促立辱警罪-梁美芬重提佔領時有幼稚園老師教幼童-黑警-仇警/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/leung2_CJb6a_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fleung2_CJb6a_1200x0.png&h=a5b1989e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經民聯立法會議員梁美芬，今午在《城市論壇》上，指有幼稚園教師在佔領期間，教小朋友警察是「黑警」，以佐證社會已出現辱警風氣，有必要設立辱警罪。<br />\n<br />\n「有啲聲稱幼稚園嘅老師，都要對住啲幼童，唔知咩事嘅兩、三歲，就話嗰啲係『黑警』，挑釁社會、特別係年輕人對警隊嘅仇恨。<br />\n<br />\n佔中期間有一幅好經典嘅圖畫，有個人自稱幼稚園老師，對住一批幼童，攞住啲圖畫，令到聽嗰啲幼童好仇恨警察囉。」<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，梁美芬的講法並不準確。佔領期間，一名幼稚園教師在金鐘海富中心，以小動物故事的形式，向小朋友講解人大落閘與佔領行動原因，當中提及警員使用胡椒噴霧、催淚彈等，令集會的「小動物」受傷等內容，並向幼兒問及「警察用暴力啱唔啱」等語；根據現場片段，該教師並無稱警員為「黑警」。<br />\n<br />\n該女教師在海富講故事的片段上載網絡後，被建制派口誅筆伐為對幼童「洗腦」，有「四點鐘許SIR」之稱的時任公共關係科總警司許鎮德批評指有人向幼童灌輸「警察是壞人」訊息，批評行為是不負責任，令該教師成為撐政府網民的攻擊對象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36vx4cG3gRw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D36vx4cG3gRw&d=WXcHt8yLUpgx7cmMWxn67QKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=23bfb5d9\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=36vx4cG3gRw</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://goo.gl/XBmn7O\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FXBmn7O&h=97f08ca7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33f89ba752b7d3975b916c766b9a4bd1b2052ce0","tid":138097,"uid":43806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T10:47:03.000Z","msg":"講事實都錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a599d70b1ca8fca99738d668ebe0574cdef9a07","tid":138097,"uid":57762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:22:33.000Z","msg":"呢啲人返幼稚園重新讀過啦，正確對同錯都唔識分<br />\n判斷力廢過幼稚園學生"},{"pid":"58ee840c2235943e79230f601f96f44378af0a92","tid":138097,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T02:43:48.000Z","msg":"係咪唔比講事實呀咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c7e7e5ed39e069367de304643df478a0d947b9","tid":138097,"uid":58983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"言論自由呀屌你老母，講事實都唔比，係咪要講你老母係男人先得"},{"pid":"10ac70c84a2d09e1c5fa9c54260875c994de57e1","tid":138097,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T03:57:37.000Z","msg":"根本班狗奴才就失哂控 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb8a991782814d8c6dc7a25c64fbc337f2266b8e","tid":138097,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T04:06:59.000Z","msg":"咁嗰七個係未警察呀？<br />\n<br />\n嗰七個警案係未打人呀？<br />\n<br />\n咁講嗰七個警案使用暴力有邊個字錯呀？"},{"pid":"d561a8c7086c4dee625c7f94db81cece3a89856d","tid":138097,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T07:16:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=